description:
The Face is an British reality television modeling competition series.

The series follows three supermodel coaches, Caroline Winberg, Erin O'Connor, and Naomi Campbell as they compete with each other to find 'the face' of the U.K.




The Face UK - Series 1, Episode 1




The Casting Call

Naomi Campbell, Erin O'Connor and Caroline Winberg evaluate 24 girls in a series of challenges before deciding on which girls they want for their team. Each of the supermodel mentors will pick 4 girls that they will mentor.




Original Air Date: 30-Sep-2013
